78},{"width":1433,"height":806,"file_path":"/q14nuxNcoHOHumnBAQ3fI2CtYIL.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1467,"height":825,"file_path":"/8NDAM9aghNhpaEXbBE5qhCLzc0N.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1382,"height":778,"file_path":"/flm2GPEZ4H6lFPT0IwsL7tg62T3.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1447,"height":814,"file_path":"/pVxKS64dFt19WI0uNoBgWtBgBvP.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1354,"height":761,"file_path":"/gu3syA5d7aTcA6A2b3A7hMzqw42.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1468,"height":826,"file_path":"/rfyLWQKemncCN2ts4Un7o5VnbGx.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1465,"height":824,"file_path":"/nlQntbAQKZ6vg9YKCfR4Mn5x3SN.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/c8NDXpoQvWXY3T4B4GofGDA5TgY.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":3840,"height":2159,"file_path":"/hAswuCESijFfcdwO81NvcMrFvnt.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/uJY5AxN1UWrrfq7z3jAPmAXODI9.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T07:03:05.133+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Legends of the Condor Heroes: The Gallants","runtime":147,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Under Genghis Khan, the Mongolian army pushes west to destroy the Jin Dynasty, setting its sights on the Song Dynasty next. Amid internal conflicts among martial arts schools, Guo Jing unites the Central Plains' warriors to defend Xiangyang, embodying courage and loyalty in the fight for the nation."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Anh Hùng Xạ Điêu: Hiệp Chi Đại Giả","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Trong giang hồ đầy ân oán tình thù, giữa thời đại chiến loạn quyền lực tranh giành, Quách Tĩnh (do Tiêu Chiến thủ vai) từ nhỏ đã rời xa quê hương, dần rèn luyện nên một sức mạnh to lớn có thể thay đổi cả cục diện và vận mệnh. Dù được các cao nhân xem trọng và truyền dạy những tuyệt học võ công như “Cửu Âm Chân Kinh” và “Giáng Long Thập Bát Chưởng”, nhưng chính điều đó cũng khiến anh trở thành mục tiêu đố kỵ của nhiều thế lực. Quách Tĩnh, khiêm nhường nhưng kiên định, giữ trọn tấm lòng trong sáng. Cùng Hoàng Dung (do Trang Đạt Phi thủ vai), anh dũng cảm xông pha giữa khói lửa chiến trường và mưa tên ngựa sắt, gánh vác sứ mệnh bảo vệ biên ải nhà Nam Tống. Giữa biển trời và chim điêu, người anh hùng không biết sợ hãi – người đại hiệp chân chính, xoay chuyển cả giang sơn, lập nên truyền thuyết võ lâm."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":146,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"恩怨情仇的江湖，权势角力的战乱时代，郭靖（肖战 饰）童年离别家乡，逐渐炼就可改变局面和命运的庞大力量。虽受高人赏识和器重，得传天下绝世武功“九阴真经”和“降龙十八掌”，却惹来各方嫉忌，成为众矢之的。  　　郭靖，不亢不卑，怀赤子之心，与黄蓉（庄达菲 饰）在铁骑箭雨和硝烟旌旗中，力挽狂澜，保护南宋边关。  　　雕海苍穹，勇者无惧，侠之大者，力拔山河，成就武林传说。  　　本片主要改编自金庸同名原著第34至40章。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"มังกรหยก จอมยุทธ์ผู้ยิ่งใหญ่","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ชาวมองโกลที่นำโดย เจงกิสข่าน มุ่งหน้าเดินทัพไปทางทิศตะวันตกเพื่อที่จะทำลายราชวงศ์จิ้น และต้องการมุ่งลงใต้เพื่อทำลายราชวงศ์ซ่ง ทำให้เหล่าจอมยุทธ์จากสำนักต่าง ๆ ในตอนกลางของจีนต้องร่วมมือกันรวบรวมพลังเพื่อปกป้องเมืองเซียงหยางเอาไว้ให้ได้"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"射鵰英雄傳：俠之大者","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"改編自金庸先生經典武俠著作《射鵰英雄傳》第 34 至 40 章，故事講述恩怨情仇的江湖，權勢角力的戰亂時代，郭靖（肖戰 飾）童年離別家鄉，逐漸煉就可改變局面和命運的龐大力量，雖受高人賞識和器重，得傳天下絕世武功「九陰真經」和「降龍十八掌」，卻惹來各方嫉忌，成為眾矢之的，郭靖不亢不卑，懷赤子之心，與黃蓉（莊達菲 飾）在鐵騎箭雨和硝煙旌旗中，力挽狂瀾，保護南宋邊關。雕海蒼穹，勇者無懼，俠之大者，力拔山河，成就武林傳説。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Легенды о героях Кондора: Храбрые","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Под предводительством Чингисхана монгольская армия продвигается на запад, чтобы уничтожить династию Цзинь, а затем нацеливается на династию Сун. На фоне внутренних конфликтов между школами боевых искусств Го Цзин объединяет воинов Центральных равнин для защиты Сянъяна, воплощая мужество и преданность в борьбе за нацию."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"La Légende des Héros du Condor","runtime":146,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"La redoutable armée mongole, menée par Gengis Khan, se met en marche vers la Chine avec pour objectif d’anéantir la dynastie Jun à l’ouest et la dynastie Song au sud. Les puissants maîtres d'arts martiaux de plusieurs écoles vont unir leurs forces pour leur faire face et devenir des héros nationaux."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Легенда за героите на Кондор","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Филмът е адаптиран по класическото произведение на г-н Джин Йонг „Легенда за героите на Кондор“. В него се разказва за свят, изпълнен с огорчение и омраза, в разкъсваната от войни епоха на борба за власт. Гуо Дзин (в ролята – Сяо Джан) напуска родния си град и усвоява изключителната мощ на бойните изкуства, за да промени съдбата си. Въпреки че е уважаван от кунгфу майстори и е завещал на поколенията ненадминатите „Наръчник на деветте Ин“ и „Осемнадесетте длани за победа над дракона“, към него се заражда завист от всички страни и той става обект на публични критики. Гуо Дзин и Хуанг Жун (в ролята - Чжуан Дафей) обръщат хода на събитията и защитават границата на династията Южна Сун сред дъжд от стрели на противници."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"射鵰英雄傳：俠之大者","runtime":146,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"恩怨情仇的江湖，權勢角力的戰亂時代，郭靖（肖戰 飾）童年離別家鄉，逐漸練就可改變局面和命運的龐大力量。雖受高人賞識和器重，得傳天下絕世武功“九陰真經”和“降龍十八掌”，卻惹來各方嫉忌，成為衆矢之的。  郭靖，不亢不卑，懷赤子之心，與黃蓉（莊達菲 飾）在鐵騎箭雨和硝煙旌旗中，力挽狂瀾，保護南宋邊關。雕海蒼穹，勇者無懼，俠之大者，力拔山河，成就武林傳說。  本片主要改編自金庸同名原著第34至40章。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"افسانه عقاب های مبارز: دلیران","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"تحت رهبری چنگیزخان، ارتش مغول به سمت غرب حرکت کرد تا سلسله جین را شکست دهد و سپس تصمیم داشت به سمت جنوب برود تا سلسله سونگ را نابود کند. رزمی‌کاران ماهر از مکتب‌های مختلف دشت مرکزی در این نبردهای سخت شرکت داشتند. قهرمانانی چون گو جینگ که نماد واقعی جوانمردی بودند، با گرد هم آوردن نیروهای جامعه‌ی رزمی دشت مرکزی، برای دفاع از شیانگ‌یانگ، کشور و مردم ایستادگی کردند."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"사조영웅전: 협지대자","runtime":148,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"오랜 세월 떠돌며 무공을 쌓다가 조국 남송으로 돌아온 난세의 영웅 ‘곽정’. 과거의 인연을 매정하게 뒤로하고 남송을 집어삼키려는 야욕을 숨기지 않는 ‘대칸’. 두 무림 강호들은 전란의 소용돌이 속에서 같은 하늘 아내 단 하나의 진정한 영웅을 가리기 위해 한치도 물러설 수 없는 전쟁을 시작한다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Bohaterowie legendy Kondora: Szlachetni mężowie","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Pod rządami Czyngis-chana armia mongolska naciera na zachód, by zniszczyć dynastię Jin, a następnie kieruje wzrok na dynastię Song. Pośród wewnętrznych konfliktów między szkołami sztuk walki Guo Jing jednoczy wojowników Central Plains, by bronili Xiangyang, uosabiając odwagę i lojalność w walce o naród."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"אגדות גיבורי העיט: אנשי החרב","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"מבוסס על הרומן בעל אותו שם מאת לואי צ'ה, אומן הסיפורת הסיני שמתרכז בסוגת אומנויות הלחימה, ובבימויו של הקולנוען האגדי הארק צוי. מתרחשת במהלך שושלת סונג (1127–1279), עלילת הסרט מתחקה אחר סיפורו של גואו ג'ינג, שגדל ונהיה אומן לחימה כדי להפוך לגיבור לאומי, ומציגה את קסמן הייחודי של אומנויות הלחימה הסיניות."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Akbaba Kahramanlar Efsanesi","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Çin’in dövüş sanatları kurgu ustası Louis Cha’nın aynı adlı romanından uyarlanan filmin yönetmeni efsanevi filmci Hark Tsui. Çin’in Güney Song Hanedanı döneminde (1127-1279) geçen film, dövüş sanatları ustası ve ulusal kahraman olan Guo Jing’in hikâyesini anlatırken Çin dövüş sanatlarının eşsiz cazibesini gözler önüne seriyor."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"A Condor hősök legendái: A vitézek","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A mongolok Dzsingisz kán vezetésével nyugatra mentek, hogy elpusztítsák a Csin-dinasztiát, és délre akartak menni, hogy elpusztítsák a Song-dinasztiát. Kína középső síkságának több iskolájából származó harcművészeti mesterek küzdöttek, összegyűjtve erejüket, hogy megvédjék Xiangyangot."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Leyendas de los héroes Cóndor: Los valientes","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Guo Jing abandonó su ciudad natal y adquirió un enorme poder en las artes marciales para cambiar su destino. Aunque era valorado por los maestros de kung fu que transmitieron las artes marciales sin parangón en el mundo \"Manual de los Nueve Yin\" y \"Dieciocho Palmas Subyugadoras del Dragón\", se formaron celos hacia él por parte de todos, convirtiéndose en el blanco de las críticas públicas. Guo Jing y Huang Rong cambiaron las tornas y protegieron la frontera de la dinastía Song del Sur en medio de la lluvia de flechas."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Lendas dos Heróis do Condor: Os Valentes","runtime":146,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A história de Guo Jing, que se tornou um mestre em artes marciais para se tornar um herói nacional, demonstrando o charme único das artes marciais chinesas."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Baserad på Louis Chas klassiska roman, med samma namn, av Kinas mästare inom kampsportsfiktion och regisserad av den legendariske filmskaparen Tsui Hark. Filmen utspelar sig under Södra Songdynastin (1127–1279) och följer Guo Jings resa från enkel krigare till stridskonstmästare och nationell hjälte. En berättelse som fångar den unika kraften och skönheten i kinesisk kampsport."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Kondoro didvyrių legenda","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Čingischano vadovaujama mongolų kariuomenė žygiuoja į vakarus, kad sunaikintų Džin dinastiją, o vėliau planuoja pulti į pietus ir sunaikinti Song dinastiją. Kovos meistrai iš įvairių Vidurio Kinijos lygumų kovos mokyklų sutelkė jėgas Šiangiano gynybai."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"67a73750ad2758bac5f10fc8","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/67a73750ad2758bac5f10fc8","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$11","created_at":"2025-02-08T10:52:00.879Z","updated_at":"2025-02-08T10:53:32.759Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":6,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":1293286,"adult":false,"title":"Gunslingers","video":false,"overview":"When the most wanted man in America surfaces in a small Kentucky town, his violent history -- and a blood-thirsty mob seeking vengeance and a king’s ransom -- soon follow. As brothers face off against one another and bullets tear the town to shreds, this lightning-fast gunslinger makes his enemies pay the ultimate price for their greed.","genre_ids":[37],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.4265,"vote_count":96,"poster_path":"/O7REXWPANWXvX2jhQydHjAq2DV.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-11","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/zksO4lVnRKRoaSYzh2EDn2Z3Pel.jpg","original_title":"Gunslingers","original_language":"en"},{"id":1190150,"adult":false,"title":"Kane","video":false,"overview":"Benny works for old school crime boss Abe, Abe has multiple personalities and is in a gang war with the notorious Frankie. Kane is the deadliest of Abe's personalities, the next 24 hours will be a killer. Today is a good day to die.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5333,"vote_count":28,"poster_path":"/A7QI9Y6lXxBson48fCo4mrxkseI.jpg","release_date":"2023-11-10","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/d07RB8bOOgKKL3HEFkrVuPFqQcZ.jpg","original_title":"Kane","original_language":"en"},{"id":25684,"adult":false,"title":"American Ninja 5","video":false,"overview":"When a scientists daughter is kidnapped, American Ninja, attempts to find her, but this time he teams up with a youngster he has trained in the ways of the ninja.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7395,"vote_count":124,"poster_path":"/feLMfivbHHla844jWrVnqgzU0Zh.jpg","release_date":"1993-04-02","vote_average":4.73,"backdrop_path":"/6Y9Gd1GBge8LMV60xhk6XCUmNMI.jpg","original_title":"American Ninja 5","original_language":"en"},{"id":746808,"adult":false,"title":"The Great Yokai War: Guardians","video":false,"overview":"Fifth grader Kei Watanabe has inherited the hunter's blood to hunt yōkai. To save the world from destruction, Kei challenges a war against the yōkai.","genre_ids":[14,10751,12,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.709,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/40As72DGjh37ZxeYXyQHIVMJ10o.jpg","release_date":"2021-07-01","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/mWcJFpg74fi1QM5W24NhNFAoOV7.jpg","original_title":"妖怪大戦争 ガーディアンズ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":246862,"adult":false,"title":"Surrender","video":false,"overview":"An erotic drama that submerges an innocent new arrival to the City of Angels in the intoxicating double life of her charismatic lesbian dominatrix housemate.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.3769,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/9myM7jwo4fKoz7TTptR4plrlLvE.jpg","release_date":"2003-03-20","vote_average":2.917,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Surrender","original_language":"en"},{"id":1365103,"adult":false,"title":"Marriage Unplugged","video":false,"overview":"Unhappy in their marriage, Suzanna and Andrew buy a male sex robot called James, who consequently uncovers the deep fractures in their relationship.","genre_ids":[878,35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8124,"vote_count":14,"poster_path":"/3H99Wl52sBPRqXZ3LJjgODOLfwX.jpg","release_date":"2024-10-28","vote_average":4.9,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Marriage Unplugged","original_language":"en"},{"id":1086011,"adult":false,"title":"All the Long Nights","video":false,"overview":"Two work colleagues: he suffers from panic attacks, she has extreme PMS. Their company distributes toy planetariums. What may not sound like Ozu Yasujirō is actually precisely that: people are attentive and do each other good, without even realising.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6795,"vote_count":31,"poster_path":"/cihErynZk0v0A0xKlMMg6tb9zfJ.jpg","release_date":"2024-02-09","vote_average":7.032,"backdrop_path":"/9TZY0Jk2G2papFIWgQzY1QwZklo.jpg","original_title":"夜明けのすべて","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1140738,"adult":false,"title":"The Bastard Sons","video":false,"overview":"Life for a crew of organized criminals is disrupted when Vincent Damiano's father, the family's boss, is murdered. Vincent's \"bastard\" brothers, a group of orphaned souls he raised together, have an idea of who killed their father...his partner Rome. In a valiant and calculated attempt to regain the business and enact vengeance on Rome, the Bastards wage an all-out war to get their pound of flesh.","genre_ids":[80,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2122,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/3qqVFa9yLSkjiL6x8F1i1pjbBGA.jpg","release_date":"2024-01-05","vote_average":4,"backdrop_path":"/83chrDJQVUtR31j312FInqHkgpu.jpg","original_title":"The Bastard Sons","original_language":"en"},{"id":1003623,"adult":false,"title":"Di Renjie and Fire Unicorn","video":false,"overview":"In the Lantern Festival, the people pray for the blessing of the Empress Wu Zetian, but a strange beast with a full body of fire appears. It is said that eating the flesh and blood of the unicorn can cure all diseases, so Wu Zetian orders the Secretary of the Da Lisi, Xue Xin, to find out the truth within seven days. When the young Dee comes to Chang'an to be promoted to the position of \"Chancellor\" of the Da Lisi, he learns of a strange case at the Shang Yuan Festival and that he needs to wait until the case is solved before he can report to the court. Dee, who had wanted to wait for his job to be solved, is intrigued by this strange case and becomes involved in it by mistake.","genre_ids":[28,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3357,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/gfFwH1M5EltlO0EzEVFwI0BS6xd.jpg","release_date":"2022-07-23","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/cL0GfO0WJYKZOJFr3mjEIlZIzbB.jpg","original_title":"狄仁傑之浴火麒麟","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1357305,"adult":false,"title":"Detective Chinatown 1900","video":false,"overview":"In 1900, a white woman was murdered in Chinatown in San Francisco, and the suspect was a Chinese man. The murder caused social shock, and people demanded the closure of Chinatown.","genre_ids":[35,9648,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.1301,"vote_count":95,"poster_path":"/g3GsgIlH3fA4RxhNOAMvSbVWyfW.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-29","vote_average":6.316,"backdrop_path":"/ux9bsXuwkhlSHwcnmKa8hzTOadO.jpg","original_title":"唐探1900","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1155281,"adult":false,"title":"Creation of the Gods II: Demon Force","video":false,"overview":"Taishi Wen Zhong led the army of Shang Dynasty including Deng Chanyu and four generals of the Mo Family to Xiqi. With the help of Kunlun immortals such as Jiang Ziya, Ji Fa led the army and civilians of Xiqi to defend their homeland.","genre_ids":[28,14,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.6133,"vote_count":128,"poster_path":"/dfUCs5HNtGu4fofh83uiE2Qcy3v.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-29","vote_average":6.371,"backdrop_path":"/yujcZMkNKtNXPvRGyTA3e3VCrbx.jpg","original_title":"封神第二部：战火西岐","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1290879,"adult":false,"title":"The Woman in Cabin 10","video":false,"overview":"On a lavish yacht for an assignment, a journalist sees a passenger go overboard. But when no one believes her, she risks her life to uncover the truth.","genre_ids":[9648,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.811,"vote_count":889,"poster_path":"/4kpdyePOlcELQQJcxXPF5GB1Adw.jpg","release_date":"2025-10-09","vote_average":6.205,"backdrop_path":"/9IHZeCusOd7RUaQpUrQJlKqjsUZ.jpg","original_title":"The Woman in Cabin 10","original_language":"en"},{"id":568467,"adult":false,"title":"Ammonite","video":false,"overview":"In 1840s England, palaeontologist Mary Anning and a young woman sent by her husband to convalesce by the sea develop an intense relationship. Despite the chasm between their social spheres and personalities, Mary and Charlotte discover they can each offer what the other has been searching for: the realisation that they are not alone. It is the beginning of a passionate and all-consuming love affair that will defy all social bounds and alter the course of both lives irrevocably.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8753,"vote_count":631,"poster_path":"/5lx4pUHWZoOKJWsVsvurRRNW9FK.jpg","release_date":"2020-11-13","vote_average":6.916,"backdrop_path":"/23wCZgZ3mDtATocmy1lXNLM7pyx.jpg","original_title":"Ammonite","original_language":"en"},{"id":755898,"adult":false,"title":"War of the Worlds","video":false,"overview":"Will Radford is a top analyst for Homeland Security who tracks potential threats through a mass surveillance program, until one day an attack by an unknown entity leads him to question whether the government is hiding something from him... and from the rest of the world.","genre_ids":[878,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":118.3382,"vote_count":897,"poster_path":"/yvirUYrva23IudARHn3mMGVxWqM.jpg","release_date":"2025-07-29","vote_average":4.205,"backdrop_path":"/iZLqwEwUViJdSkGVjePGhxYzbDb.jpg","original_title":"War of the Worlds","original_language":"en"},{"id":1061474,"adult":false,"title":"Superman","video":false,"overview":"Superman, a journalist in Metropolis, embarks on a journey to reconcile his Kryptonian heritage with his human upbringing as Clark Kent.","genre_ids":[878,12,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":30.2198,"vote_count":4360,"poster_path":"/ldyfo0BKmz5rWtJJKCvwaNS4cJT.jpg","release_date":"2025-07-09","vote_average":7.362,"backdrop_path":"/aJDLz1748CIMZkCkyISYe5Hl6I7.jpg","original_title":"Superman","original_language":"en"},{"id":522402,"adult":false,"title":"Finch","video":false,"overview":"On a post-apocalyptic Earth, a robot, built to protect the life of his dying creator's beloved dog, learns about life, love, friendship, and what it means to be human.","genre_ids":[878,18,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.9724,"vote_count":3845,"poster_path":"/eEJtzD1F05xDipFEDY98CTH5yZn.jpg","release_date":"2021-11-04","vote_average":7.812,"backdrop_path":"/uoc358GH6Yl7TufbUKHkETPu64B.jpg","original_title":"Finch","original_language":"en"},{"id":290859,"adult":false,"title":"Terminator: Dark Fate","video":false,"overview":"Decades after Sarah Connor prevented Judgment Day, a lethal new Terminator is sent to eliminate the future leader of the resistance. In a fight to save mankind, battle-hardened Sarah Connor teams up with an unexpected ally and an enhanced super soldier to stop the deadliest Terminator yet.","genre_ids":[878,28,12,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.4741,"vote_count":5545,"poster_path":"/vqzNJRH4YyquRiWxCCOH0aXgg